 raids are not mandatory and are viewed more as a social gathering with the bonus being loot.<br><br>On August 2nd the Legion of Light will turn three as a guild and two in Everquest this shows our members commitment to the guild and the strength that our mission gives us.<br><br>If you are interested in the Legion please visit our website at http://www.thelegionoflight.net or http://www.legionoflight.net we are also happy to answer any questions you may have either in game, on our forums or you can contact me (Glamm) via e-mail at glamm@legionoflight.net.<br><br>I leave you with our guild charter.<br><br>-We, of the Legion of Light are sworn to valor. Our hearts know only virtue. Our blades defend the helpless and our might upholds the weak. Our words speak only truth and our wrath undoes the wicked that creeps throughout the land.   <br><br>-Norrath is our home. We are explorers, adventurers, hunting companions, questers, traders, tutors, and artisans. Our pleasure comes from championing the Light, stretching our abilities, sharing with others, laughing, and having fun.   <br><br>-We are a diverse group and in that lies our strength. We are bound by a code of honor, good sportsmanship, strength of arms, teamwork, and loyalty. Join us!  <br> <p><center><a href="http://www.legionoflight.net"><img src="http://www.thelegionoflight.net/Sigs/Glammsig8.jpg" border="0"></a><br><font size="2">"This foe is beyond any of you...run!" - Gandalf</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uavalynightstar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Avaly Nightstar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/9/02 9:15:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fprexus95980guildrecruiting.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=415.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://bestanimations.com/Natur